<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٥٩٩)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">اسْمُ أَبِي زُرْعَةَ:</span> كُنْيَتُهُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَدْ قِيلَ:</span> اسْمُهُ هَرِم<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>